'''硝酸钌(III)'''是一种[[无机化合物|无机化合物]]，[[化学式|化学式]]为Ru(NO<sub>3</sub>)<sub>3</sub>。它可用于制备钌碳催化剂。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Journal of Catalysis|volume=229|issue=1|language=en|date=2005-01-01|pages=176–184|doi=10.1016/j.jcat.2004.10.020|url=https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S0021951704005123|title=Particle growth behavior of carbon-supported Pt, Ru, PtRu catalysts prepared by an impregnation reductive-pyrolysis method for direct methanol fuel cell anodes|accessdate=2019-06-17|author=T Kawaguchi, W Sugimoto, Y Murakami, Y Takasu|archive-date=2018-07-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180703045940/https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S0021951704005123|dead-url=no}}</ref>硝酸钌负载在二氧化硅上之后，和一氧化碳反应，根据反应条件的不同，会生成Ru(CO)<sub>2</sub>(OSi)<sub>2</sub>、Ru(CO)<sub>3</sub>(OSi)<sub>2</sub>以及Ru<sub>3</sub>(CO)<sub>12</sub>。<ref>Huang, L.; Xu, Y. IR spectroscopic study on surface-​mediated reductive carbonylation of hydrated SiO2-​supported Ru(NO3)​3. ''Catalysis Letters'', 2001. 71. (1-2): 27-30. ISSN: 1011-372X.</ref>

